Fables - A collection of four 7-minute Film Operas, created by Streetwise Opera performers working with some of the most exciting composers and filmakers in the UK. Tonight will screen the four films, 'The Making of' documentary a Q&A with the film-makers and a live performance by the local Streetwise group." data-bind="attr: { content: summary }"/>
